text: Carthage is a city in the U.S. state of Missouri. The population was 15,522 at the 2020 census. It is the county seat of Jasper County. It is nicknamed "America's Maple Leaf City."Carthage, Missouri Chamber of Commerce - America's Maple Leaf City! ==References== Category:County seats in Missouri Category:Cities in Missouri Category:Jasper County, Missouri
